We have this in a form:

<div class="field">
  <%= f.label :name %><br>
  <%= f.text_field :name %>
</div>
<div class="field">
  <%= f.label :price %><br>
  <%= f.text_field :price %>
</div>
<div class="field">
  <%= f.label :description %><br>
  <%= f.text_area :description, rows: 5 %>
</div>
<div class="field">
  <%= f.check_box :discontinued %>
  <%= f.label :discontinued %>
</div>

Lots of repitition:  field, label, input


Yikes!